+# Reachy_Local_08.3 — Requirements Addendum v0.08.3.3 (2025-10-06)
+
+This appendix documents updates introduced since v0.08.3.2.
+It does **not** alter prior content; treat it as an incremental layer until full merge.
+
+## 1. Summary of Changes
+- Pinned TAO Toolkit container to `nvcr.io/nvidia/tao/tao-toolkit:6.25.9-pyt`
+- Defined workspace mounts and environment variables (`~/.tao_mounts.json`)
+- Canonicalized video storage path on Ubuntu 1 (`/media/rusty_admin/project_data/reachy_emotion/videos`)
+- Added endpoint map for Ubuntu 1 (10.0.4.130) and Ubuntu 2 (10.0.4.140)
+- Clarified ActionRecognitionNet schema (`model.sample_length` deprecated)
+- Confirmed Media Mover FastAPI runs on Ubuntu 1
+
+## 2. Storage and Mounts
+**Physical root:** `/media/rusty_admin/project_data/reachy_emotion/videos`
+**Logical root:** `/videos/{temp,train,test,thumbs,manifests}`
+
+Example `~/.tao_mounts.json` file:
+```json
+{
+  "Mounts": [
+    { "source": "/media/rusty_admin/project_data/reachy_emotion", "destination": "/workspace/reachy" },
+    { "source": "/home/rusty_admin/tao_specs", "destination": "/workspace/specs" },
+    { "source": "/home/rusty_admin/tao_output", "destination": "/workspace/output" }
+  ],
+  "Envs": [
+    { "variable": "PROJECT_ROOT", "value": "/workspace/reachy" },
+    { "variable": "VIDEOS_ROOT",  "value": "/workspace/reachy/videos" }
+  ]
+}
+```
+
+## 3. Component Roles
+- **Ubuntu 1 (10.0.4.130):** Media Mover API, Nginx static media, PostgreSQL, TAO training, MLflow (optional)
+- **Ubuntu 2 (10.0.4.140):** Gateway API + Web frontend; proxies to Ubuntu 1; WebSocket bridge to Jetson client.
+
+## 4. Service Endpoints
+**Ubuntu 1** (`http://10.0.4.130`)
+- Media Mover FastAPI → `:8081`
+    - `GET /api/videos/list?split={temp|train|test}`
+    - `POST /api/manifest/rebuild` → returns `dataset_hash`
+- MLflow UI → `:5000`
+- PostgreSQL → `:5432`
+- LM Studio (local LLM) → `:1234/v1/chat/completions`
+
+**Ubuntu 2** (`https://10.0.4.140`)
+- Gateway API → `/api/*` (proxies to Ubuntu 1)
+- WebSocket cues → `/ws/cues/{device_id}`
+
+## 5. Schema Notes
+If training fails with:
+```
+Error merging 'ar_train.yaml' with schema
+Key 'sample_length' not in 'ARModelConfig'
+```
+Remove the `model.sample_length` entry and set clip/window controls under dataset settings supported by your TAO AR schema.
+
+## 6. Security and Transport
+- JWT authentication for mutating endpoints between Ubuntu 2 → Ubuntu 1
+- Idempotency header (`Idempotency-Key`) on POST requests
+- Firewall allow-list for Ubuntu 1 ports: `8081, 5432, 1234, 80, 443`
+
+## 7. Quick Verification
+```bash
+curl -s "http://10.0.4.130:8081/api/videos/list?split=temp&limit=3" | jq .
+curl -s -X POST "http://10.0.4.130:8081/api/manifest/rebuild" \
+    -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" | jq .
+```
+
+## 8. Nginx Mapping Example
+```nginx
+location /thumbs/ {
+  alias /media/rusty_admin/project_data/reachy_emotion/videos/thumbs/;
+  add_header Cache-Control "public, max-age=3600";
+}
+location /videos/ {
+  alias /media/rusty_admin/project_data/reachy_emotion/videos/;
+  internal;
+}
+```
+
